Section.name: About Ashoka Women's Engineering College
Section.description:
Ashoka Women's Engineering College, the biggest Women's Engineering College in Rayalaseema was established in 2008 by Dr. K.V. Subba Reddy Garu, an eminent educationalist. The Institution is promoted by Vishwam Educational Society, Allagadda, Kurnool District. It aims to become an excellent centre in providing globally relevant education and be a benchmark institution for lifelong partnerships with students, the workforce, and public and private enterprises.
